        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-10-24T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-10-24T16:00:00-05:00" n="354" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d354">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">701.6132/10–2447: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Key</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-10-24T18:00:00-03:00">October 24, 1947—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1471. Moscow’s 3084, October 23 to Department.<note n="23" xml:id="d354fn1">Not
                        printed.</note> Called on Secretary General Foreign Office at noon today and
                    drew his attention to complications created by inadequate police protection of
                    Soviet Embassy premises Rio. I expressed hope that no further similar incidents
                    would occur and enquired whether precautions were being taken in view of the
                    large demonstration of solidarity scheduled for this afternoon in front of
                    Catete Palace and danger that some of participants might afterwards demonstrate
                    before Soviet Embassy. <pb facs="0417" n="401" xml:id="pg_401"/> Accioly stated
                    that he would immediately telephone police to post adequate guard around Soviet
                    Embassy premises.</p>
                <p>Department relay Moscow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Key</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
